how we can help

 

why choose us
we are the oldest and largest cremation society in the state. we own and operate our own equipment meaning we personally oversee the care and disposition of your loved one from start to finish. they never leave our care.
learn more

 

our cremation process
our state-of-the-art cremation equipment meets all environmental standards. we also follow a thorough bar code identification process.
learn more

 

when death occurs
you will feel comfort knowing that we are here to walk you through this inevitable journey of grief every step of the way.
learn more

 

testimonials
we are committed to providing support, compassion, information, & guidance as needed to all of those in need in the community.
